Class DBWhereOperator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ecoinformatics.seek.querybuilder.DBSelectTableModelItem
      • org.ecoinformatics.seek.querybuilder.DBWhereListCellBase
        • org.ecoinformatics.seek.querybuilder.DBWhereOperator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.datatransfer.Transferable, DBDisplayItemIFace, DBWhereIFace, DSTableFieldIFace

    public class DBWhereOperator
extends DBWhereListCellBase
    A boolean operator class that can "contain" one or more conditions (DBWhereCondition). cond AND cond AND cond
    An operator contains a "closure" object that used for the sole purpose of showing where the operator containment ends in the UI.
